  "3326230": {
    "name": "焕家物语 (Hozy)",
    "steam_appid": 3326230,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/34bafa9ae318e76ac61c6c666ca919a1.avif?t=1772208296\" width=780 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在大城市遭遇挫折后，你回到了宁静的家乡小镇。这里曾经充满活力，如今却略显褪色、被人遗忘。但在寂静中，你发现了意外的惊喜：一份新的热爱。一个房间接一个房间，一套公寓接一套公寓，你清洁、粉刷，温柔地修复着曾经充盈街巷的邻里温情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/5da470767111877ae0419cc8372139af.poster.avif?t=1772208296\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/5da470767111877ae0419cc8372139af.webm?t=1772208296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/5da470767111877ae0419cc8372139af.mp4?t=1772208296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/2c33480adc416bbac66504344c3d54bf.avif?t=1772208296\" width=780 height=65 /></span>这是一款让人放慢节奏的游戏。没有计时器，没有分数，没有惩罚，也绝对没有压力。只有你，你的工具，以及让各种空间重现美丽的简单快乐。无论是擦拭窗户、重新粉饰墙壁，还是为沙发选择一个绝佳的摆放点，所有的事物都是为了让你沉浸在这种宁静而满足的节奏中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/d5c118b4b49b41a69f0fd0e84348f302.poster.avif?t=1772208296\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/d5c118b4b49b41a69f0fd0e84348f302.webm?t=1772208296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/d5c118b4b49b41a69f0fd0e84348f302.mp4?t=1772208296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/f66653095605820ec2539db89904d06e.avif?t=1772208296\" width=780 height=65 /></span>沉浸在这舒适的氛围中，每个细微的动作和细节都值得用心感受。推开窗，让清风与浮尘共舞，将自然的声响带入室内。点亮烛光，在书架上摆好书册，在墙上绘一幅肖像，或是打开投影仪……你所触碰的每件物品、所做的每个选择，都会带来满满的成就感与轻柔的惊喜感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/c4b530dc3e7aa4d3e2952267d5f7312a.poster.avif?t=1772208296\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/c4b530dc3e7aa4d3e2952267d5f7312a.webm?t=1772208296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/c4b530dc3e7aa4d3e2952267d5f7312a.mp4?t=1772208296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/3f2ee35c56111c6f2e40531849ff7454.avif?t=1772208296\" width=780 height=65 /></span>《焕家物语》呈现了九处风格各异的空间，等待你探索与修缮。每个角落都镌刻着居住者的生活印记，从珍藏记忆的独特物件到饱含巧思的细节陈设，处处流淌着鲜活的生活气息。从父母的老宅启程，踏入艺术家的创作工坊，再探访满载旧日时光的咖啡馆——穿越这些如梦似幻的房屋，最终为父亲实现他长久以来的愿望，在海滨建设一处宁静天地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/f94bae23fa26acd396c49ffaec26280b.poster.avif?t=1772208296\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/f94bae23fa26acd396c49ffaec26280b.webm?t=1772208296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/f94bae23fa26acd396c49ffaec26280b.mp4?t=1772208296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/4a191f2548f75a43cb4c4b1d84480b3c.avif?t=1772208296\" width=780 height=65 /></span>跳过繁多的目录。《焕家物语》为每个关卡精心挑选风格协调的家具与软装，供你随心搭配。自由旋转、移动和摆放物品——这里没有标准答案，每一处空间都将成为独一无二的创作。明智地使用你手中的工具，就能打造出媲美室内设计杂志的完美空间！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/80dd17566977a21e2802d0f8323cea2b.poster.avif?t=1772208296\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/80dd17566977a21e2802d0f8323cea2b.webm?t=1772208296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/80dd17566977a21e2802d0f8323cea2b.mp4?t=1772208296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326230/extras/3b3368ffd61e815931ae5d03a795b043.avif?t=1772208296\" width=780 height=65 /></span>-可供修缮的多样空间，没有任何限制，可以完全跟随你的步调重塑空间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-丰富多样的清洁与翻修工具，如拖把、玻璃刮、撬棍等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-基于物理的清洁玩法，带来深度满足感</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-精心挑选家具与装饰，以达到风格协调，搭配美观</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-由创意自由与游戏细节驱动，重玩性无穷</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-多功能拍照模式，支持滤镜与高级镜头控制</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-由《Stray》和《Seasons After Fall》作曲家创作的原声音轨，迷人动听</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 韩语, 波兰语, 俄语, 日语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西",
